metadata.name: Genesis F-CLAIM
metadata.description:
The 'f'-collective is a diverse group of individuals coming together to create something "INTERESTING". 

PAK has demonstrated countless ways to innovate in this industry, many participants have absorbed and transformed this information into many new 'f'orms; f-1 DROP is one of them. 

Each 'f' collective NFT is designed by a unique creator, and some are rarer than others. When you collect one of our digital items, you may have the chance to join our community. More information will be shared later, Browse the collection below, find a piece that speaks to you and be the first to own some art from the 'f' community.

https://www.fcollective.art/
